{
  "stem": "27335.6",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in Europe, we are waiting very impatiently in-- in Italy, in San Vito what-- what-- what-- what will happen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the situation was such in-- in-- in Hungary-- the Germans occupied in Hungary, in March 1944.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they did-- Hungary became-- became a lion's cage that-- that there-- there was no news from there, and so on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had to wait for and opportune moment how to get-- get into Hungary.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And finally, on the last days, in August, 1944, all of sudden a national uprising took place in Slovakia under-- under the leadership of General Golian.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was-- he was a colonel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But then the-- the Czech government from-- from London the-- the [INAUDIBLE] government, said they promoted him to-- to a general right away.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, two days later-- two days later, we landed-- landed in Slovakia not very far from [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And from there, with the personal-- personal care and help of General Golian-- he organized-- he organized my way.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He-- he knew the importance of it because he checked out in-- in London also.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then he was do everything, get everything you can in the fastest way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he organized-- he organized my-- my crossing the border with a trusted partisan.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so, he led-- led me over in one of the-- one of the nights.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And into-- into [INAUDIBLE], at the time, because that part, you know, it was re-annexed at-- was given by Hitler to-- to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then there, I-- I waited a whole week.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And with-- with the-- with the contact there, he was also a Jew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the reason he wasn't deported, because he was the only electrician.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
